 and other revenue\nmanagement strategies, and to guide resource allocation to mitigate consumer\nsurplus impacts due to disruptions from incidents.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 19 Dec 2019 03:31:18 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Sat, 10 Jul 2021 02:23:15 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-09-07"}
