 phase and amplitude damping errors. Our work\nprovides fundamental insights and makes significant progress towards the\nestimation of multiple incompatible observables.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 19 Dec 2019 14:28:55 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 27 May 2020 17:38:45 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Thu, 6 Aug 2020 08:00:19 GMT"},{"version":"v4","created":"Sun, 31 Jan 2021 23:14:17 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-02-17"}
