ance of data consistency. A suitable trade-off between perceptual\nimage quality and quantitative scores are achieved with the ensembled\n$\\Sigma$-net.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 18 Dec 2019 16:52:39 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-12-20"}
